'''铁(III)酸锂'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为LiFeO<sub>2</sub>。它可由草酸铁锂（Li<sub>3</sub>[Fe(C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>]·5H<sub>2</sub>O）在600 °C时的热分解制得。<ref>Barb, D.; Mihaila-Tarabasanu, D.; Diamandescu, L.; Turcanu, C.; Florescu, I. Moessbauer and x-​ray studies of solid lithium trisoxalatoferrate(III) thermolysis. ''Radiochemical and Radioanalytical Letters'', 1978. 33 (5-6): 373-379.</ref>[[碳酸锂|碳酸锂]]和[[氧化铁|氧化铁]]的反应也能制得铁(III)酸锂。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Ceramic Society|volume=59|issue=3-4|language=en|issn=0002-7820|date=1976-03|pages=171–172|doi=10.1111/j.1151-2916.1976.tb09463.x|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1111/j.1151-2916.1976.tb09463.x|title=Kinetics of Formation of LiFeO2 from 2Li2CO3 Fe2O3Mixtures|accessdate=2020-09-26|author=P. K. Gallagher, D. W. Johnson}}</ref>

